Chicago 90
game.desc: "Priority call - Central to all cars - Hold up on 12th Street - suspects heading east in a red interior driver's license CHGO90. Warning, armed and dangerous suspects! Intercept them by all means before they leave the city. I repeat: Dangerous suspects to be intercepted by all means! Over and out". Choose your side: gangsters or police. Your goal: to get out of the city as quickly as possible if you are a gangster and to successfully intercept the thieves if you are in uniform. Skids, stunts, accidents... nothing will be spared you! Strong emotions and thrills guaranteed! A real action game but also a strategy game. With CHICAGO 90 you will have to study the movements of the different police vehicles by choosing the level of difficulty that suits you.

Super Ski
game.desc: With SUPER SKI, go full steam ahead on the slopes. Slalom, Downhill, Giant Slalom and Ski Jumping : SUPER SKI offers you the most prestigious alpine skiing events on the best competition slopes ! SUPER SKI is a 3D ski simulator with impressive speed and unmatched realism! Beware of spectators, trees... collisions are often dangerous! Put on your best pair of skis, choose your event, your slope and fight against the stopwatch in a simulation where everything is possible ... without the risk of a fracture.
